Package: ezyros
Version: 1.0.0
Section: utils
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash, curl, lsb-release
Maintainer: cosmic399
Description: Zero-friction ROS2 installer for Ubuntu
 EzyROS auto-detects your Ubuntu version, selects the right
 ROS2 distro, and handles all repos, keys, and configuration
 in one command.
